ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲學人做文豪"},{"pid":"e51fc1d0ecd65d6fcf259634ce075211ccf8f63a","tid":2300489,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c735ac3993fbf1fe91702f447b8f89dd2cab45","tid":2300489,"uid":281802,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"最令人心灰意冷嘅唔係西方左膠，而係本地左膠，即係撐敗登嘅人，如果侵真係輸咗，真係唔會同呢班本地左膠行落去。"},{"pid":"471084523da44290f2b2e2ad31dd06f202bedbb3","tid":2300489,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f52a5590c9cb41b2900af6ec54f034851864fd","tid":2300489,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:37:37.000Z","msg":"你講下就爽<br />\n你話可以對自己好啲<br />\n只係因為出事嘅唔係你<br />\n你唔搞落去<br />\n出左事嘅邊個理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e482fbeac6bf835c7e900afc3face78216b729","tid":2300489,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">死後世界<br />\n係香港唯一既替代品</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"655b553c1444e545d13983e6b4e0752a55385b61","tid":2300489,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"染紅嗰部分講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n但<span class=\"red\">前設</span>係外國唔會以疫症對付中國，侵輸咗又唔開戰，中印，南海唔走火，中國内鬥比雜種解決哂"}]}